Hi Tim & Clementine,
Just go ahead and weld up your hitch for it to be U-bolted to the torsion bar 
tube.  That way when you need to tow other heavy objects you can do so with 
no worries.  Believe us when we say once you have a hitch you will find (or 
perhaps they find you) things to tow!
